      lang=EN-US>KindEditor&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>
      </span>熟练使用<span lang=EN-US>MySQL</span>数据库<span lang=EN-US>,</span>了解<span
      lang=EN-US>Oracle</span>数据库<span lang=EN-US> <br>
      </span>熟悉<span lang=EN-US>Nosql</span>型数据库<span lang=EN-US>Redis <br>
      </span>了解<span lang=EN-US>SOA</span>的思想和实现，了解基于<span lang=EN-US>Dubbo+ZooKeeper</span>实现表现层与业务层解耦，了解使用<span
      lang=EN-US>ActiveMQ</span>进行分布式系统间的异步通信<span lang=EN-US><br>
      </span>了解<span lang=EN-US>SolrCloud</span>及其客户端<span lang=EN-US>Solrj</span>的使用，了解<span
      lang=EN-US>Redis</span>集群及其客户端<span lang=EN-US>Jedis</span>的使用<span
      lang=EN-US><br>
      </span>了解<span lang=EN-US>nginx</span>服务器，了解<span lang=EN-US>FastDFS</span>图片服务器，了解<span
      lang=EN-US>Linux</span>常用命令</p>
